Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...because you are my treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.04,0:00:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...because your eyes\Nare my treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,THE FINAL BATTLE!\NSAVE ASUKA JR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.08,0:00:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. hasn't come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been absent\Nfor four days already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he disappear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the police\Nare looking for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he really is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister! How is Detective Asuka?\NAsuka's father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka's father is on\Na top-secret mission right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we can't contact him...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran for my life\Nfrom the monastery...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. didn't come\Nto the place in my warning note.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, he was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.59,0:01:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...missing...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Takamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably\Nscrewed up somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Asuka is Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he must be eating\Nwhen he needs to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...and he must be sleeping\Nwhen he needs to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll pop up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been four days since I was\Nlocked in the top of this tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hide\Nthe truth from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you enjoying teasing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you think of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.06,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. didn't show up\Nat the warning note's location...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he see the warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maju said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you search,\Nthe detective won't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! Does this mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...Asuka Jr. was captured\Nby the mother and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.31,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're punishing me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...to get their revenge\Non Mom and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting him back?!\NYou mean Asuka Jr.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's the same\Nas telling him your identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you'll get caught!\NThen you two will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.37,0:04:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.41,0:04:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I can't be\NSt. Tail anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...he's an important\Nperson to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he may hate me,\Nor I may not be able to see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I want him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use trying\Nto stop you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be praying for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. This is\Nthe only method I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please deliver this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...Meimi has never\Nstolen anything for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time...\Nno, only this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...please protect\NMeimi and Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God\Nbe with the two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.40,0:05:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It has something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's coming here soon, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are going as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypnotized the police\Nand sent them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will come to this\Nmonastery and disturb us, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.55,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NEverything is in order here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucifer's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you suffering soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you planning\Nto keep me locked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Until Mom says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about that. Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my house, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. is here, isn't he?\NLet him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a foolish girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...I would simply hand him over?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pretty picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How long is this hallway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep running...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...until your heart bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The end...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.61,0:08:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find the end of the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing delivered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:08:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a stupid thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's deliberately come here\Nto be defeated by Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight I'm going to\Nthe monastery to get Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.57,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!\NGive him back... Give him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste for your talent\Nto be stuck in such a small town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how Maju joined me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't my real daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us and grab\Nall of the treasure in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.13,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Jewels and art...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can live in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What I want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My jewel is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:11:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So that boy is\Nyour 100-carat diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you aren't very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a hallucination.\NIt's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This warning note...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When did it come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a love letter, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are so dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The other notes until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get caught by you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not a princess\Nlocked up in a tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stand by\Nwithout doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please protect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...is telling me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. is in that tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Butterfly powder is mixing\Nwith my jade dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! It's so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the time! Grab the keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! There used to be\Na bridge to the other tower!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to save others!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My silk hat...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I'm St. T...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,God is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender and go quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What about our revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had met someone\Nlike him 20 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...who loved me no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go to the next town\Nand make some money, Maju!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...St. Tail disappeared\Nfrom Seika City.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she had been caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,8 YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to save\Nanother lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We owe it all to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I shouldn't call you\NJunior anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a full-fledged\Nprivate investigator now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I'm not used to it yet.\N- Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka! Don't steal work\Nfrom the police!
